{"tid":1042970,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"BMW 大改款測試車 1-Series 車廂照曝光","createTime":"2019-03-02T02:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T02:44:48.000Z","uid":236926,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"cc80766600240b54ea2acdfe2d2a480fc314996c","tid":1042970,"uid":236926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"[From <a href=\"http://car1.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcar1.hk&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=2ac889d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">car1.hk</a>]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/100735_ecbe14c7bec7ed2aec5f824a773ae420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F100735_ecbe14c7bec7ed2aec5f824a773ae420.jpg&h=d911ee28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/100803_e301239e086f886e69a8dbf1b17f0e0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F100803_e301239e086f886e69a8dbf1b17f0e0c.jpg&h=2552e359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/100818_0693ec1bd182954f1ab2dbe96a95b6e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F100818_0693ec1bd182954f1ab2dbe96a95b6e1.jpg&h=6ccbf855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了對抗 Mercedes-Benz A-Class，BMW 不得不加緊腳步，早前大改款 1-Series 進行測試時就「不小心」被拍下車廂照。大改款 1-Series 的 B 柱車尾線條更斜，帶來更強的跑感；外觀造型暫時所知，將會使用更大型鬼面罩和全新 LED 頭尾燈組。另外，以 FAAR 平台所打造，由舊款的後驅改為前驅，不過車身尺碼將會變大，帶來更寬闊的乘坐空間。至於車廂設計方面主打 iDrive 雙大型螢幕和導入最新世代智慧娛樂系統對抗 Mercedes-Benz 的 MBUX 系統。大改款 1-Series 預計在今年 9 月的法蘭克福車展正式亮相。"},{"pid":"f0ec2015abacd5ceb7822f03f7f9d9c41bfb5297","tid":1042970,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:15:29.000Z","msg":"好似係用M35i偈"},{"pid":"636e24d2133966807bf44085e4d86bf76f0