,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"新款寶馬完全係抄benz+lexus，柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:15:01.000Z","msg":"好撚難服侍<br />\n轉又話抄<br />\n唔轉又話寶馬食老本，一成不變正垃圾<br />\n唔中意咪唔買<br />\n你鬧佢柒佢都唔會專登幫你度身訂造"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T10:27:32.000Z","msg":"話佢唔靚就係屌佢轉款?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢今代學晒benz夾硬谷大個豬鼻懶有霸氣，車尾又成部lexus咁，係得個側線仲似返架寶馬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:34:58.000Z","msg":"咁都要佢轉款你先有機會屌佢唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋大豬鼻不嬲都每代大一些，你睇翻E世代去F世代都大好多<br />\n<br />\nBtw新1系個側線最唔似寶馬...<br />\n<br />\nL字型尾燈寶馬都其實用咗好多年...係凌志抄翻佢先啱<br />\n<br />\nE32 7系係第一款用L型尾燈嘅寶馬<br />\n<br />\n同期嘅凌志LS你google吓睇吓尾燈咩樣，係普通一塊長方型<br />\n<br />\n所以啲人屌新3系尾燈抄凌志我都係得啖笑，根本未分清莊閒"},{"pid":"bc91705ea177dde21939b9a93bc7ff8307ac053c","tid":1042970,"uid":32901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"後座咁撚窄"},{"pid":"591f4db24f17b859fbce803c7cf6286727f84125","tid":1042970,"uid":99124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:46:37.000Z","msg":"頭轆bmw仲叫唔叫bmw"},{"pid":"9234addacb48236c67affe09f521200ae8d846da","tid":1042970,"uid":26536,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"591f4db24f17b859fbce803c7cf6286727f84125","tid":1042970,"uid":99124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:46:37.000Z","msg":"頭轆bmw仲叫唔叫bmw"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/195429_139ed5dcf1b8b34264e3ff1599d067be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F195429_139ed5dcf1b8b34264e3ff1599d067be.png&h=e02d52ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bb8adf617d3f82fd8b6a46e77f378458bcf3e5a","tid":1042970,"uid":14073,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"591f4db24f17b859fbce803c7cf6286